{"tid":1550332,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"唔講笑 d歌對藍絲好大影響","createTime":"2019-09-07T15:34:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T16:18:28.000Z","uid":261157,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8a843a7af25efa35720c900b4172f57cf9a4bd95","tid":1550332,"uid":261157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:34:00.000Z","msg":"上次講到我屋企人由深黃變淺藍<br />\n<br />\n屋企人由極深黃變成淺藍<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1531570\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1531570</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n唔理我屋企人係深黃好淺黃好，我都堅持令我屋企人改變番立場。之後我每次都會播d連登仔自創嘅反送中歌。琴晚俾我屋企人聽個首《願榮光歸香港》之後，我屋企人竟然會心微笑，仲要有種感動嘅感覺。<br />\n<br />\n所以，我喺呢度想打番個關於呢場運動嘅歌list, 大家一定要聽、背熟，最重要係播俾身邊d藍絲聽，感化下佢地。最重要係一定要整多d歌，除左感染佢地之外，自己無力個陣都可以振奮下。<br />\n<br />\n歌list:<br />\n《願榮光歸香港》<br />\n《香港之歌》<br />\n《和你飛》<br />\n《香港人》<br />\n《沙燕之歌》<br />\n<br />\n如果巴絲打有咩好歌介紹都可以推介下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5bc93de1adeebb3eef7646ec6b49659a39e1448","tid":1550332,"uid":261157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:34:20.000Z","msg":"P牌冇得推"},{"pid":"222b7a4e10ee3335e5c74e413f8708964d1e8d1d","tid":1550332,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:34:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">出黎呀，自由閪！</div></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不闖入、不塗鴉、不鐳射</strong></span></span><br />\n如有發現，批淮大家往死裡打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明日之公眾集會(遮打花園)及公眾遊行(前往美領)已獲發不反對通知書。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n集會部分<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n時間：13:30 - 18:30<br />\n四節主題：時代子民、獄中讚歌、審判將至、天佑美國<br />\n<br />\n※※ 遮打現場將收集香港人權與民主宣言聯署至14:30﹐隨後出發向美領遞交 ※※<br />\n<br />\n遊行部分<br />\n集合地點：中環遮打花園金鐘道出口<br />\n集合時間：14:30<br />\n遊行路線：遮打花園經花園道往下亞厘畢道巴士站公眾活動區，向美國領事館遞交請願信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZY3Vs7C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZY3Vs7C.jpg&h=2d1d3d5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"71dbeef7b463f651fcdddf7928dfcb77ea6b251f","tid":1550332,"uid":261157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:34:47.000Z","msg":"咁多位幫手推下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8db0e2848b29863124debbd6bf56c5a8bf5704f3","tid":1550332,"uid":261157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:35:12.000Z","msg":"感化身邊藍絲呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7b7dcc85ad9c7f478f8ad3a022b9e1435719210","tid":1550332,"uid":74567,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:35:50.000Z","msg":"香港人真係聽一次喊幾次"},{"pid":"b1a0e24ec41290a14aee13ceb2845ff48ff4e12b","tid":1550332,"uid":261157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e7b7dcc85ad9c7f478f8ad3a022b9e1435719210","tid":1550332,"uid":74567,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:35:50.000Z","msg":"香港人真係聽一次喊幾次"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:36:02.000Z","msg":"係超感動"},{"pid":"c97e437b01fe9fa19a6e259f7c0ae512b236416d","tid":1550332,"uid":261157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b1a0e24ec41290a14aee13ceb2845ff48ff4e12b","tid":1550332,"uid":261157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e7b7dcc85ad9c7f478f8ad3a022b9e1435719210","tid":1550332,"uid":74567,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:35:50.000Z","msg":"香港人真係聽一次喊幾次"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:36:02.000Z","msg":"係超感動"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:36:17.000Z","msg":"仲要配埋mv冇得頂"},{"pid":"de58a1089faa91f70ea7ddcf8c4528116a726d02","tid":1550332,"uid":261157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:38:36.000Z","msg":"D歌都可以係文宣嘅一種方法呀"},{"pid":"b2bdf6dbef26f341e12a404797e38d4227781b26","tid":1550332,"uid":138934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":